{
  "stem": "1858.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody helped us by supplying us with the barest necessities, such as food, to keep our souls intact, to keep our mind working.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also, you must take into consideration that if you are 18, or 17, or 19, and you are ready to die for a cause, you must take into consideration that if you should be caught you definitely will die, and you are prepared for it.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you also must be able to bear the responsibility that if you get caught, your whole family will also be wiped out, and sometimes a whole village.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Which was the case in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One, one young man killed one German soldier, and the whole village was wiped out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it wasn't easy just to go and fight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a boy who was my best girlfriend's brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His whole family was taken away, and he was the only one that remained.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother ask him if he would like to come and stay with us, but he chose not to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he saw that there was no room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had only one bed in that room that was for my mother, my father, my younger sister, and myself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got used to, already, living in the street, I guess with other boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think maybe he felt more comfortable there than in a family unit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, he, like everybody else, perished, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- because of-- you know, because of the constant raids of the Nazi raids, people began building bunkers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, no matter what, you always want to make it one more day, always hoping that tomorrow it will end.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In our case, we built also a bunker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was in the basement of the building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a windowless wall.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
